  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Army should also be equipped for cyber warfare",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe said that Sri Lankan war heroes should be equipped with the necessary knowledge for such a technological war, as wars may take place not only on the ground, in the air, but also in cyberspace.",
        "The President said that discipline training and knowledge are needed to create a successful army and said that the Sir John Kotalawala Defense University is fulfilling all these matters.",
        "The President said this while participating in the ceremony held this afternoon (25) for the awarding of the Presidential Colors and University Colors to General Sir John Kotalawala Defense University."
      ],
